#### BOSH CLI v2: Viewing statistics

To view usage statistics for any service, select the service broker deployment.
Then run `bosh2 vms --vitals` and `bosh2 instances --vitals` to view current resource utilization.

You can also view process-level information by using `bosh2 instances --ps`.

